<section class="section page-header page-header-compact">
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/library" class="back-link">← 返回课件库</a>
        <div class="view-header">
            <div>
                <div class="view-meta">
                    <span class="courseware-subject <%= courseware.subject %>"><%= courseware.subject %></span>
                    <span class="courseware-grade"><%= courseware.grade %></span>
                </div>
                <h1><%= courseware.title %></h1>
                <p><%= courseware.description %></p>
                <div class="courseware-tags">
                    <% courseware.tags.forEach(function(tag) { %>
                    <span class="tag"><%= tag %></span>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="view-actions">
                <a href="/download/<%= courseware.id %>" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                    <span>⬇ 下载课件</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section view-preview">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="preview-frame-wrapper">
            <div class="preview-toolbar">
                <div class="toolbar-dots">
                    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                </div>
                <span class="toolbar-title"><%= courseware.title %></span>
                <div class="toolbar-actions">
                    <a href="/download/<%= courseware.id %>" class="toolbar-btn" title="下载">⬇</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <iframe src="/<%= courseware.file %>" class="preview-frame" loading="lazy" title="<%= courseware.title %>"></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section view-info">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>📖 使用说明</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>本课件为独立 HTML 文件，双击即可在浏览器中打开</li>
                    <li>支持所有现代浏览器（Chrome、Edge、Firefox）</li>
                    <li>无需网络连接，下载后离线也可使用</li>
                    <li>可直接发送给学生或投屏到课堂上展示</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>🎯 教学建议</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>引导学生动手操作，观察参数变化对结果的影响</li>
                    <li>结合课件中的交互功能进行课堂提问</li>
                    <li>可作为课后复习工具发给学生自主探索</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
